This torrent has a few issues.  First, it says Theta, but it does not use a Theta installer.  Second, the installer is not in English which is not typical for a Theta release.  The game works, but I would advise caution when downloading this as the torrent uploader has done this in the past as well (labeling releases as Theta that don't actually include a Theta installer).
